Brigitte Sy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brigitte_Sy 0 Brigitte Sy (born 26 January 1956) is a French actress and filmmaker. Her directorial film debut, Les Mains libres, was released in 2010 to critical acclaim in France. Brigitte_Sy ( born 26_January_1956 ) is a_French_actress_and_filmmaker .
